import React from 'react'; import '../Css/MobileFilter.css'; import all from '../Images/5110770.png'; import Laptops from '../Images/Laptop.png'; import GamingLaptop from '../Images/GamingLaptop.png'; import Desktops from '../Images/Desktop.png'; import accessories from '../Images/ComputerAccessories.png' import smartwatch from '../Images/smartwatchs.png'; import Camera from '../Images/camera.png'; import headphones from '../Images/headphones.png'; import others from '../Images/Other.png' const FashionFilter = ({ selectedSubCategory, selectedPrice, onSubCategoryChange, onPriceChange }) => (
onSubCategoryChange('')}>
All
onSubCategoryChange('Laptops')}>
Laptops
onSubCategoryChange('GamingLaptop')}>
Gaming Laptops
onSubCategoryChange('Desktop')}>
Desktops
onSubCategoryChange('Computers')} /> Desktops
onSubCategoryChange('ComputerAccessories')} /> Accessories
onSubCategoryChange('Headphones')} /> Headphones
onSubCategoryChange('Smartwatch')} /> Smart Watches
onSubCategoryChange('Camera')} /> Cameras
onSubCategoryChange('Others')} /> And More
onPriceChange(parseInt(e.target.value, 10))} />
{selectedPrice} /-
); export default FashionFilter;
